<p><strong>Q: What are the key strategic management concepts covered in the 3rd edition?</strong>
<strong>A:</strong> The textbook covers a wide range of topics, including strategic analysis, strategy formulation, strategy implementation, and strategic control. It also delves into specific issues facing organizations in Southern Africa, such as culture, governance, and ethics.</p>
<p><strong>Q: How are the concepts applied in real-world scenarios?</strong>
<strong>A:</strong> The textbook features numerous case studies that provide practical examples of how companies in Southern Africa have successfully applied strategic management principles. These case studies cover various industries and sectors, offering valuable lessons and insights.</p>
